Revision history for Lang::JA::Kana

1.0.0  2025-06-11
    - Initial release
    - Complete modern Hiragana/Katakana conversion support
    - Historical and obsolete kana support (ゐゑ, ゔ, ゟ)
    - Comprehensive Hentaigana (historical variant) support with multiple readings
    - Modern extensions for foreign sounds (ファ, ティ, ウィ, etc.)
    - Half-width Katakana support (complete Unicode range U+FF65-U+FF9F)
    - Half-width voiced and semi-voiced combinations (ｶﾞ→ガ, ﾊﾟ→パ)
    - Half-width punctuation and sound mark conversion
    - Circled Katakana support (㋐㋑㋒ ↔ アイウ)
    - Square Katakana support for technical terms (㌔㌦ ↔ キロドル)
    - Sound mark splitting and Hentaigana conversion with dakuten/handakuten handling
    - Intuitive Hiragana/Katakana prefix operators
    - Mixed text handling (only converts kana, leaves other text unchanged)
